raying at two sacred mosques","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn al-Zubayr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPrayer in this mosque of mine is better than a thousand prayers in any other mosque, except the Sacred Mosque. Prayer in the Sacred Mosque is one hundred times better than prayer in this mosque\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28535,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/30\/salat-women-masjid-haram-nabawi\/","url_meta":{"origin":5635,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: Best prayer for women at home, except sacred mosques","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Amr al-Shaybani reported: Ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cNo woman performs prayer in a better place than her house, except if it is at the Sacred Mosque or the Mosque of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 9472 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18460,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/07\/salat-bayt-al-maqdis-al-quds\/","url_meta":{"origin":5635,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jerusalem: Pray in Masjid al-Aqsa, or send gifts","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 7, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Maymunah repor